{"tid":1646053,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有冇得諗】學何妖咁改歌詞，整返首《反赤納粹之歌》","createTime":"2019-10-11T06:42:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T09:08:30.000Z","uid":94168,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cf3d587746c11a51496a7c69e31b8eb060078dd9","tid":1646053,"uid":94168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T06:42:59.000Z","msg":"之前何妖搵人改咗《願榮光》啲歌詞，在擺咗上網嘅，雖然首歌好快落咗架，但係佢嘅做法其實都值得我哋學習，因為有一首歌其實我哋一直都未搞過佢，就係：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">中国國歌</span><br />\n<br />\n因為依首歌，其實而家喺香港仲會係無可避免咁係唔同場合咁播出嚟，之前我哋嘅做法都只可以係噓佢或者唔啱音咁疊住佢咁唱其他歌；但係如果我哋可以將啲歌詞改左佢，變成一首《反赤納粹之歌》，令到佢好似願榮光咁hit大家都識唱，咁之後大家就可以響任何奏中国國歌嘅場合唱依set歌詞啦<br />\n<br />\n預期效果：<br />\n1) 唱到佢連國歌都唔敢播<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2) 激嬲中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3) 搞到政府要即刻用緊急法立埋國歌法，加速外國制裁同攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家覺得可唔可行？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔識改歌詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeebff04af46dc9c83e85424d1b047ac1aad0c3d","tid":1646053,"uid":94168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T06:49:54.000Z","msg":"自推 一成"},{"pid":"ca5fba54c6ce22615b9d5de06f3ec67c9a65caee","tid":1646053,"uid":94168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T06:50:44.000Z","msg":"自推 兩成"},{"pid":"77e03281b7e06ef8e2360996dc63e67b50481b5f","tid":1646053,"uid":94168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T06:51:31.000Z","msg":"自推 三成"},{"pid":"4b195adabb543c19a758116832b4564e6e429677","tid":1646053,"uid":94168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T06:52:40.000Z","msg":"自推 四成"},{"pid":"e8fe3a24818d16911282ee52feb2cebffe052ece","tid":1646053,"uid":62343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T06:53:09.000Z","msg":"起來 不願做奴隸的人們"},{"pid":"581f152adfde886f0148fc0f89204c253fbf8549","tid":1646053,"uid":